sp.p:
An inviting eye;
and yet methinks
right modest.

What, man! 'tis a night of revels;
the gallants
desire it.

No, I hear not your honest friend;
I
hear you.

I will catechize the world for him;
that is, make
questions, and by them answer.

So hangs, and lolls, and weeps upon
me;
so hales, and pulls me: ha, ha, ha!
